'''Fudgie Frottage''' ({{IPAc-en|icon|ˈ|f|ʌ|dʒ|i|_|f|r|oʊ|ˈ|t|ɑː|ʒ}}) is the stage name of American drag performer, producer and community activist Lu Read who is based in [[San Francisco]].<ref name="Perform, Bend, Twist, Pull">{{cite web |last=Hix |first=Lisa |title=Perform, Bend, Twist, Pull: Drag king contest: Contestants feel free to reshape gender any which way they want |publisher=[[SF Chronicle]] |date=2006-08-17 |url = http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2006/08/17/NSGDOIM5561.DTL&hw=lu+read&sn=001&sc=1000 |accessdate=2007-07-27}}</ref> Ms. Read, as Frottage, is well known in San Francisco's gay and lesbian community as a club promoter and event producer.<ref name="San Francisco Erotika">{{cite web |last=Ehmann |first=Abby |title=San Francisco Erotika: Fudgie Frottage |publisher=Eros Zine |date=2005-06-07 |url = http://eros-guide.com/articles/2005-06-07/fudgie0607/ |accessdate= 2007-07-28 |archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20070704095106/http://eros-guide.com/articles/2005-06-07/fudgie0607/ |archivedate = 2007-07-04}}</ref> Read as Frottage also [[emcees]], produces and acts as a judge for local drag contests.<ref name="Drag King Contest Brings Out">{{cite web |last=Van Iquity |first=Sister Dana |title=Drag King Contest Brings Out Fierce Competitors |publisher=[[San Francisco Bay Times]] |date=2005-08-25 |url = http://www.sfbaytimes.com/?sec=article&article_id=4033 |accessdate=2007-07-27}}</ref> Frottage is credited as having played "Cop No. 1" in El Presidente, an independent film<ref name="El Presidente The Movie: Cast List">{{cite web |title=El Presidente The Movie: Cast List |publisher=ElPresidenteTheMovie.com |year=2006 |url = http://www.elpresidentethemovie.com/presskit.htm |accessdate=2007-07-28}}</ref>
